        "additional_details": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/LGBT_rights_in_Uganda\r\n\r\nhttp://www.washingtonblade.com/2016/04/22/report-anti-lgbt-persecution-increased-under-uganda-law/\r\n\r\nhttp://www.huffingtonpost.com/the-groundtruth-project/inside-the-nightmares-of_b_7674502.html\r\n\r\nhttp://rainbowrailroad.ca/whatwedo\r\n\r\nhttp://www.hias.org/work/resettling-refugees\r\n\r\nhttp://hamiam.de/en/\r\n",
